      | &ldquo;We&rsquo;re importing your contact list from Skype for Business Online to Teams. Now, all your contacts and groups that you created in Skype for Business will show up in Teams under your contact list. To access your contacts, simply click on &ldquo;Chat&rdquo; in the left navigation and then on &ldquo;Contacts&rdquo;. Here, you can also add new contacts or create new contact groups.
    blockquote
      | In this first step, only contacts from your organization will be imported. Federated contacts from outside your organization will be added at a later point.&rdquo; - 
      a(href='https://techcommunity.microsoft.com/t5/Microsoft-Teams-Blog/What-s-new-in-Microsoft-Teams-April-update/ba-p/179801') Microsoft
    p
